  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Haryana</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Haryana has four seasons: cold winter (Nov–Feb), scorching summer (Apr–Jun), monsoon (Jul–Sep) and a brief pleasant spring (Mar). October to March is the golden window — Kurukshetra is best in winter, the Surajkund Crafts Mela is in February, wheat fields turn golden in March and wildlife sanctuaries are at their finest.</p>
